194
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:06,360
<span tts:color="yellow">Cleaning the car.
No. Keeping the teapot warm.

195
00:17:06,360 --> 00:17:12,000
<font color="yellow">No!</font> Not really! That's a Debbie
joke. <font color="yellow">Is that a Debbie joke?</font> Yeah.

196
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:18,240
<font color="lime">This is Louis Theroux.</font> <span tts:color="yellow">You're Chris
and you own the theatre. </span> 'Fraid so.

