00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:23,000
And you donated two weeks
of the theatre space. <font color="lime">Three.</font>

198
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:28,320
I haven't told her what she's gotta
do yet! We're negotiating. <font color="lime">We are.</font>

199
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:35,040
<span tts:color="yellow">Oh, my God, there's a...
</span> <span tts:color="lime">A swan. We're trying this out.
