201
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:45,000
Can't do better. <span tts:color="yellow">Congratulations.
</span> I could kiss everybody.

202
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:50,440
I think it's great that they've sold
out with a new company. Fabulous.

203
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:52,960
Here it comes again.

204
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:03,320
It hasn't got any feathers on,
but we're still not sure about it.

205
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:08,640
If ever that falls over,
you're in major schtuck.

206
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:18,560
David, could you do that again...?

207
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:21,720
Who's doing that? How is it moving?

208
00:18:23,320 --> 00:18:28,080
We have a...
<font color="lime">We don't look at things like that!</font>

209
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:30,600
We don't film things like that.

210
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:37,640
<font color="lime">That takes away the magic.</font> Don't be
ridiculous. <span tts:color="lime">People don't want to
know it works. They don't.

211
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:43,160
